' logical expression could make the dependencies of useEffect Hook (at line 152) change on every render. Move it inside the useEffect callback. Alternatively, wrap the initialization of 'transactions' in its own useMemo() Hook.","React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'summaryTotal' and 'theme'. Either include them or remove the dependency array.",["1450"],"The 'accounts' logical expression could make the dependencies of useEffect Hook (at line 157) change on every render. Move it inside the useEffect callback. Alternatively, wrap the initialization of 'accounts' in its own useMemo() Hook.",["1451","1452"],["1453","1454"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'resetState'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["1455"],["1456","1457"],["1458","1459"],["1460","1461"],"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'syncMutation'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["1462"],"@typescript-eslint/no-require-imports","A `require()` style import is forbidden.","CallExpression","noRequireImports",{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1464","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1467","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1469","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1470","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1471","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1472","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1473","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1474","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1475","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1476","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1477","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1478","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1479","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1480","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1481","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1482","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1483","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1484","desc":"1468"},{"messageId":"1463","fix":"1485","desc":"1465"},{"messageId":"1466","fix":"1486","des